snippet.title: AFTER-H : LEGEND OF MARS - Trailer (EN)
snippet.description:
After-H : Legend of Mars - Chapter 1: The artifact
VR FPS coop mission (free-roaming)

You are sent to Mars on a recon mission but nothing is going according to plan. Strategy, collaboration and communication are your best tools to get out of there alive...
